WEBVTT

00:14:29.630 --> 00:14:31.285
Dahshatli tengsizlikda yashaymiz.

00:14:31.285 --> 00:14:33.486
Ha, dunyoda tengsizlik mavjud,
lekin ma'lumot-

00:14:33.486 --> 00:14:35.811
-larga qarasangiz, 
birgina do'nglik mavjud.

00:14:35.811 --> 00:14:37.665
Agar ikkilansangiz,

00:14:37.665 --> 00:14:40.418
"ko'pchilik aholi o'rtamiyona" 
degan variantni tanglang.

00:14:40.418 --> 00:14:42.401
Bu to'g'ri javob berishingizga
yordam

00:14:42.401 --> 00:14:46.108
beradi.
Keyingi xato tushuncha quyidagicha:

00:14:46.108 --> 00:14:49.733
davlatlar va odamlar 
ijtimoiy taraqqiyotga erishishi,

00:14:49.733 --> 00:14:52.059
qizlarini maktabga yuborishi
va tabiiy ofatlardan

00:14:52.059 --> 00:14:55.510
himoyalanishi uchun 
juda boy bo'lishlari kerak.

00:14:55.510 --> 00:14:57.196
Bu mutlaqo xato.

00:14:57.196 --> 00:14:59.316
O'rtadagi ulkan do'nglik
qizlarning maktab

00:14:59.316 --> 00:15:01.759
ta'limi allaqachon ta'minlanganini
ko'rsatadi.